    <h3 class="shortBio" ><a href="speaker/jennifer_hickey.htm">Jennifer Hickey</a>
      - <em>Senior Software Engineer at SpringSource</em></h3>
    
    
    <div class="image">
      
      <a href="speaker/jennifer_hickey.htm">
